Description_lang: The caster charges towards the Butcher. The first player to come within 2 yards of the caster will force the caster to explode for $163047s1 Physical damage to all players within $163047A1 yards. This same explosion will occur if the caster reaches the Butcher.
AuraDescription_lang: Will explode on contact with the Butcher or any player within 2 yards.
